Feature: API testing for Create and Update functions

elements.name: Create a new item using API

steps.name: I have a valid API endpoint for creating items
I send a POST request to create a new item with data:
the response status code should be 201
the response should contain the created item details

elements.name: Update an existing item using API

steps.name: I have a valid API endpoint for updating items
there is an existing item with ID "123"
I send a PUT request to update the item with ID "123" with new data:
the response status code should be 200
the response should contain the updated item details
